      "heading": "XDD/XDC",
      "level": 2,
      "content": {
        "paragraphs": [
          "CANopen® objects can refer to parameters in XDD/XDC files. These parameters can have labels in different languages. While reading a XDD/XDC the label of the parameter is displayed with the selected language. The same language is used for saving."
